<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>Open Redirect 방어 버전</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-16 p-8 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">🔒 Open Redirect 방어</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm text-center">
      “http://” 혹은 “https://” 로 시작하고, 화이트리스트에 등록된 호스트만 허용합니다.
    </p>

    <form action="/lesson/open_redirect_secure/redirect" method="get" class="space-y-4">
      <input
        type="text"
        name="url"
        value="<%= target %>"
        placeholder="https://example.com/page"
        required
        class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition"
      >
        안전 링크 생성
      </button>
    </form>

    <p class="text-center">
      <a href="/lesson/open_redirect" class="underline text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800">
        ← 취약 버전으로 돌아가기
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>